Package: gymR
Title: Simple Fitness and Gym Utility Functions in R
Description: A lightweight R package that provides simple fitness calculation tools such as one rep max estimation, protein intake recommendation, and BMI categorization for gym users and beginners interested in fitness tracking.
Version: 1.0.0
